message: <Let/> will not be reactive if Let changes. Use <svelte:component this={Let}/> if you want this reactivity.
<ExportLet/> will not be reactive if ExportLet changes. Use <svelte:component this={ExportLet}/> if you want this reactivity.
<Reactive/> will not be reactive if Reactive changes. Use <svelte:component this={Reactive}/> if you want this reactivity.
